text: KBPT-LP is a low power radio station in Bishop, California. It is owned by BIshop Paiute Tribe. ==History== KBPT-LP began broadcasting on May 29, 2015. ==References== ==External links== * Category:2016 establishments in California Category:Bishop, California BPT-LP BPT-LP Category:Radio stations established in 2016
